ion-inputs/test-build-reports/final-coverage/test-build-report.md` with PASS\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase06_profile_capabilities_verification_test.cj`\n\n**Commands run**\n- Read/narrow-context inspection:\n  - `current-agent-input.md`\n  - `plan.md`\n  - `plan.json`\n  - `translation-quality-summary.json`\n  - source profile/test files\n  - target profile/startup/test files\n- Validation/search:\n  - searched target for weakening-signal terms like `Coming soon`, `placeholder`, `stub`, `todo`\n  - searched matrix for affected feature rows and stale endpoint references\n- Authority tooling:\n  - `patch_authority.py --help`\n  - attempted narrow matrix patch via `patch_authority.py`\n- Verification:\n  - `git diff -- translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`\n\n**Remaining deferred or open gaps**\n- No new deferred gaps were introduced for this cluster.\n- The broader whole-project structure findings still exist at report level around concentrated shell endpoints and UI surface concentration, mainly outside this prompt’s profile/test working set.\n\n**Recommendation**\n- Another implementation-focused final coverage pass is not needed for this cluster.\n- One report-refresh/final verification pass is still useful so generated summaries can reflect the corrected authority evidence and any already-completed structure cleanup elsewhere.","time":{"start":1782713848885,"end":1782713859189}}}
